WEBVTT

00:10:27.538 --> 00:10:30.628
you no longer have
the right to be surprised

00:10:30.652 --> 00:10:32.483
when things don't turn out well.

00:10:33.319 --> 00:10:35.053
Stop being perplexed

00:10:35.077 --> 00:10:36.703
or confused

00:10:36.727 --> 00:10:38.203
or befuddled

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:40.606
by the achievement gap,

00:10:40.630 --> 00:10:41.853
the income gap,

00:10:41.877 --> 00:10:43.496
the incarceration rates,

00:10:43.520 --> 00:10:48.567
or whatever socioeconomic disparity
is the new "it" term for the moment.

00:10:49.248 --> 00:10:51.690
The problems we have as a country

00:10:51.714 --> 00:10:53.797
are the problems we created as a country.

00:10:54.740 --> 00:10:58.278
The quality of your education
is directly proportionate

00:10:58.302 --> 00:11:00.160
to your access to college,